{
  "texts": [
    "In this study, we have shown how Generative AI-Based Experimentation (GABE) can be a powerful tool for extending management theory.",
    "Firstly, we validate that LLMs can closely approximate human behavior in strategic group settings.",
    "In our replication of the lab experiment in Hoelzemann et al. (2024), AI agents showed a similar tendency to cluster around safer but sub-optimal choices.",
    "This demonstrates GABE's potential to extend the theory of the streetlight effect by simulating exploratory experiments.",
    "More importantly, we actively implement several of these extensions."
  ]
}